{"tid":1067373,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"天下嘅老母係咪都一樣？","createTime":"2019-03-18T13:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T10:59:59.000Z","uid":29689,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f2083aea5fdce7317a9c90bc68c409cba2189e9","tid":1067373,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T13:02:24.000Z","msg":"只要讚一次佢煮某樣野好食<br />\n(其實都唔係特登讚只係佢問到好唔好味隨口答ok)<br />\n佢就日日煮嗰樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我細個奶過一次野就學精左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢同事就慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知讚過佢煮啲咩糕好食<br />\n而家佢日日煮來帶俾佢啲同事做早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢啲同事叫佢唔洗日日煮啦咁辛苦<br />\n佢反而越煮越起勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係鄧佢啲同事可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔敢話食厭又唔敢大聲嗌唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cb02ea9e99c4b931094cbb543612f05b2d9cbb","tid":1067373,"uid":199613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T13:13:34.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢仲可以夠膽問日日食同樣既野唔厭架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b4246ab08a0bcbe7e64d223e95460136f027d4","tid":1067373,"uid":225849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T13:33:31.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n嗌極佢都唔肯日日煮蕃茄炒蛋畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a464daaeee79a8a24be5b3bc03155b731ea2cf","tid":1067373,"uid":81204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T10:57:48.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好鐘意食老母整嘅瑞士雞翼，叫佢整多d仲鬧鳩我食得多唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},